---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { site, links } from '@/data/site';

const lastUpdated = 'June 4, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`Terms of Service | ${site.shortName}`}
  description="The terms governing use of tenorcreative.com and engagements with Tenor Creative LLC."
  path="/terms"
  noindex
>
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="font-mono text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none">
        <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using tenorcreative.com or services from {site.name}
          (&ldquo;Tenor Creative,&rdquo; &ldquo;we,&rdquo; &ldquo;us,&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;),
          you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you disagree with any part, you
          may not use our services.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Our Services</h2>
        <p>
          Tenor Creative is a technical build arm providing software and systems services,
          including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom software and SaaS development;</li>
          <li>Business process automation and AI tooling;</li>
          <li>Infrastructure, DevOps, and security hardening;</li>
          <li>Technical consulting;</li>
          <li>White-label technical subcontracting for agencies.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Engagements</h2>
        <p>
          This site is provided for informational purposes. Nothing on it constitutes an offer
          or a binding quote. Any project, retainer, or advisory engagement is governed by a
          separate written agreement that controls in the event of any conflict with these
          Terms.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Payments</h2>
        <p>
          Fees, schedules, and refund terms are defined in your engagement agreement. Where
          card payments apply, they are processed through a third-party payment processor. You
          agree to provide current, accurate billing information.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          We retain ownership of our methodologies, internal tooling, and site content. You
          retain rights to your business data and to the contracted deliverables as defined in
          your engagement agreement. We may use anonymized, aggregated data to improve our
          services.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Prohibited Activities</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Engage in illegal activities or violate third-party rights;</li>
          <li>Compromise system security or disrupt services;</li>
          <li>Send spam or unsolicited communications through our systems;</li>
          <li>Reverse engineer any proprietary technology.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Analytics and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
          We use Cloudflare Web Analytics, which is cookieless, for aggregate performance
          tracking, as described in our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Disclaimers</h2>
        <p>
          Services and site content are provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; without warranties of any
          kind. We do not guarantee specific outcomes. Third-party integrations are subject to
          their own terms.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, we shall not be liable for indirect,
          incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of this site or our services.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Termination</h2>
        <p>
          We may suspend or terminate access immediately for violations of these Terms. Upon
          termination, your right to use the services ceases immediately.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Oklahoma. Disputes will be
          resolved in the courts of Oklahoma.
        </p>

        <h2>12. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may modify these Terms with 30 days&rsquo; notice. Continued use after changes
          take effect constitutes acceptance.
        </p>

        <h2>13. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>For questions about these Terms:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> {site.name}, {site.location}</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>14. SMS Program Terms</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Program description:</strong> upon opting in to the SMS service, you can
          expect to periodically receive messages from Tenor Creative.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            You can cancel the SMS service at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong>. After
            you send &ldquo;STOP,&rdquo; we will confirm your unsubscribe via SMS, and you will
            no longer receive SMS messages from us. To rejoin, sign up again as you did
            initially.
          </li>
          <li>
            If you experience issues with the messaging program, reply with the keyword
            <strong>HELP</strong>, or email
            <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a>.
          </li>
          <li>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</li>
          <li>
            Message and data rates may apply for messages sent to you from us and to us from
            you. Message frequency varies.
          </li>
          <li>For privacy-related inquiries, refer to our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          These Terms constitute the entire agreement between us regarding use of this site. If
          any provision is unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain valid. Our failure to
          enforce any right does not constitute a waiver.
        </p>

        <p>
          Looking for marketing or web services? See our sister agency,
          <a href={links.ppmc} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PPMC</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
